School play? Or Rugby.. Rugby.. or school play. OR NEITHER?!

TODAY.

I was going to go in Rugby. But I couldn't sign up since my rents were gone. I still might be though. Woo-hoo. Plus Andy, Donnie, John && my dad said how'd I'd get my ass kicked and how I'm too little. Thanks for the support!

I went to Alex's house and worked on this project thing.. yay.

Then I went to Klapprich's with John Adams Turnbull. wh00t, wh00t. That's my best bud right there. It's an ice skating rink.. hockey && whatnot. Yeah.

I'm cold && I got alot of homework. Just thought I'd make a public update. Peeace ooout!

Okay.

Walking to the library with Colton && Cake. I pushed Cake earlier, he said he'd get me back.

BOOM. WAIST TACKLED. Fly riiiight into the ice snow with John ontop of me. Fucking scared the shit out of me, that's what.

I wish I saw what that looked like from a distance.
Huh. Does anybody else feel like they have been used and/or excluded from things lately? I DO.

Megz got me lotion, knee socks, jelly bracelets. && Ally gave me a bag of candy. I got Andy Jackass, Bethany a revolver pillow and sweatband (I'm SO over you), Ally pants & shoelaces, Megan a boombox pillow with matching..thingy, Kenz a shirt & belts. Colti a shirt, Evan a shirt. Dunno if I should give them to him or not, could be throwing gas on the fire.

WHOA. I haven't had a public entry in a long time. That's because I've had so much shit going on that I just don't reveal to the public.

Well. Let's see. TOOODAY I got in a fight with Cake, Colti & Robbers. What's new, right? Hmph. I am good with Colti now, but I'll work on Cake. I don't really care for Rob. That was mean. Ha. Yeah I had another little crying game with Cake. I'm so sensative.

Huh. I downloaded like 456897 songs since I'm at my dad's. I love this computer. His CD burner is broken though. JESUS FUCK. He better get it fixed. Annnnnd. I lost. Let's see.. 13 lbs. since moving to Wayzata? WOW. WHAT A FATASS.

I'm really tired. Just downloading music. I think I might go shopping tomorrow. Huh. I ALSO LOST MY CELL PHONE. e58v79g I have to go search in the snow for it. I hope I find it. I like.. dropped it in five inches of snow and couldn't find it. Then it got shoveled away. Grr. 

CHRISTMAS COMING UP. BETTER HOPE YOU'RE ON MY GOOD SIDE SO YOU CAN GET A DAMN X-MAS GIFT.

I am like sobbing right now so I'll make it quick.

Well, that was about it. I am crying over John.

John.

...

John. Why? I don't know.

My life is spiraling downward. I couldn't get enough money to go to the Blood Red Romance and Suffocate Me Dry Concert. It sucks cause they play some of my favorite songs like "Stab My Heart Because I Love You", and "Rip Apart My Soul", and of course, "Stabby Rip Stab Stab." AND it doesn't help that I couldn't get my hair to do that flippy thing either, like that guy from that band could do, some days you know. . .

My life is just a black abyss, you know, it's so dark. And it's suffocating me! Grabbing ahold of me and tightening it's grip, tighter than a pair of my little sister's jeans . . . which look great on my by the way.

My parents just don't get me you know. They think I'm gay just because they saw me kiss a girl. Well, a couple of girls. But I mean, it's the 2000's. Can't 2, or 4 chicks makeout with each other without being gay? I mean, guys dig that kind of thing anyways. I don't know diary, sometimes I think you're the only one that gets me, you're my best friend. . . .

Wow. I feel like tacos.

You're a Playful Kisser
Kissing is a huge game for you, a way to flirt and play You're the first one to suggest playing spin the bottle at a party Or you'll go for the wild kiss during a game of truth or dare And you're up for kissing any sexy stranger if the mood is right!
What Kind of Kisser Are You?
Uh-huh. I am such a whore with my kisses even though I've kissed lips with one guy.

MMKAY.

I went to Harry Potter this fine evening with Miss Megan Carlson. And like, a half hour before the movie was done some bitches cellphone kept rining that was sitting next to me. So to be a good citizen, I opened my cell and double checked to see if my phone was on vibrate. Now, all the sudden I feel a pushing on my seat, so me & Megan turn around and this broad goes, "Turn your FUCKING CELLPHONE OFF." I was like.. "It's on vibrate, bitch."

Seriously. It was so funny. So then I kept my phone open for a few more minutes and played with it just to be a bitch. Hand in hand, the movie was okay but yeah. Then after the movie we bumped into Andrew Waters, T.A. and a few others kid I knew from school.

Then when I was standing there, that same lady pushed past me and said, "EXCUSE ME." And I was like, "Bitch." I mean, she's like 45. For one, why is she at Harry Potter? And for two, she shouldn't be yelling and being immature like that. RIGHT? Right.

I also got my picture back today. They didn't turn out very good, a few did but I wasn't satisfied. People can't take pictures. Parker took one of me, Kenzie, Bethany, and Rachel but it cuts off at our chins. lmao. A good one that turned out is the one of me & Robbers. I love it. I'll scan a few of them when I fix my scanner. I have the Rob one on here though, thanks to the power of my cellphone.

OTHER THAN THAT. I have to jet, cause Andy-poo wants me to call him. omgzz. L8er, g8ers.

TEST RESULTS: ----------- You love most: Andy You love but won't work out: Johnny-Cake You care about most: Betsy Knows you best: Colton Lucky star: Megan Andy's song with you is: Feel Good Inc. - Gorillaz Johnny-Cake's Song with you is: Hung Up - Madonna Always on your mind: Maps - Yeah Yeah Yeahs Life Song: Helena - My Chemical Romance WOAH. FIRST OFF. THIS IS BOLOGANA. Becccccause. I don't love Andy most. I lovez my Johnny-Cake, that's pretty correct. I care most about Betsy of course, but I originally put Todd. Haha. Colton doesn't know me best but hey. My lucky star? I don't even know what that is. Andy Feel Good Inc? Haha. I am not waiting for Johnny-Cake to call me all the time. Trust me, with that Hung Up song. Maps? Yeah. Pretty much my song I always think about. And my life song? I don't think it's Helena. But hey. It was pretty accurate.

I went to the mall today. That's about it. And I got a hot new hat. So yay.

Other than that, nothing. Really. I was going to go to HP with Megan but she got grounded before we were suppose to go. So grr. We'll try to go tomorrow. I just hung out with Todd/Sean/Britt. Todd is awesome. Britt is my sister, and Sean is annoying and embarrasing to go out in public with. Sad, right? Haha.

Todd bought me a new hat. I LOVE IT. Did I mention I got new kicks, too? OHMY. Love these kicks. Black/Red with broken hearts. They are freaking awesome. And with my hat, I took a picture and Sean/Todd/Zach said I look like a model with it. Uhh.

What do ya think about that hot stuff right there? I might go horse back riding tomorrow too. Not sure, but hey. WE'LL SEE. And ROOOOOB BETTER CALL ME BACK.

HERE IS THE PICTURE:

http://i7.photobucket.com/albums/y297/pawtracks/hat.jpg

We need to do that shit again. Not the cop part, but the rest would be okay. Maybe next time we can get caught making out in the woods. NOW THAT would be hilarious. "STOP, police!"

If you're wondering Emily, I went to Andy's house and people were throwing eggs and rocks and stuff at cars for fun, and the police thought we were doing it and got busted. So it pretty much sucked. I ran back to Andy's house, tracked mud on the nice carpet, and the po-po saw me I think. So we got questioned and stuff, but we got off the hook. Thank the HEAVENS.

ANYWAY.

CONGRATULATIONS ANDY! Andy, I know it's hard being a teen parent. But whatever you do, do NOT drop out. Keep on fighting, I know you want to get a job and support little Andy Jr., but you need to stay in school. Just stick next to Austin and support her. IT'S A BOY! - Bethany

Dammit. I knew this pregnency would lead into problems. Oh well. I'll have to get the kid scrambled. And I missed out showering with Andy. Shucks.

WOW.

Who had fun last night? Anyone? ..Cause I did. WOO-HOO. Alright, I saw Saw II with John & nobody else. Andy is really sick still (haha) and the movie was awesome/twisted like that last one. I still like Domino better though. Have you ever been to rottentomatoes.com? It's a movie rating site with critics and shit. AND THEY DON'T KNOW WHAT THEY ARE TALKING ABOUT. Screw em'.

Then after the movie John played this boat game in the arcade and I was laughing so hard. He gets super into it and puckers his face up, it's hilarious. Oh my. Then we had to wait for my mom, since she was late as usual. She had to sneak out of the theater, since she had to drop Brittany off at work. If she got caught, we would have got kicked out. It being rated R and all. Then after she picked us up, we went to Greenwood 'Carnival'. Kenzie, Bethany, Evan, Colton (who ditched us) Zach, Derick, and Tess were there. And a few people I didn't know. I met Derick and Chris for the first time so yay.

Hmm. John and Derick got their hair done 'wacky style', that was hilarious. John had a moehawk and it was red and blue. And Derick looked like a greaser/dalmation. Ahahaha. The rest of the night was just screaming, piggy back rides, candy, pole dancing, and all that good stuff. It was fun, so yayzz. Then I got a ride home with Derick & John. And that's the END.

AND MY PICTURES. Yeah, they turned out hot. Like 5 of them didn't turn out though. So ): But uh, I need to bring another camera because in my pictures it is practically all the same people. Andy, Bethany, Kenzie, Evan, Bethany P. And me of course, because I'm so sexy.

PEACE OUT. A TOWN DOWN?

Why?

I was getting so excited for Friday (tomorrow) then Andy goes and gets sick. My luck, hmm? Maybe magically he will like.. get better and his mom will let him prance off to school & Saw II. Otherwise it's just me & John, or not going at all. Not sure if John would go with just me. I dunno. Of course the first person to offer to bring me is Mom. I feel bad not wanting to go with her, but I just want to go with my friends. So yeah.

Anyway, I did my band-aid project. It's really sexy, it's the best paper I've ever written. Besides my Trip Story, which I got a B+ on. Actually, I got an A on my story, it is just that my map sucks hardcore. Haha. My map skillzz aren't l337. And.. I'm really tried. Nothing else went on today, I am EXCITED for my pictures to be devolped though. I am like "omgz, yay. picturezz!" YESSS. I could dance. I got really good ones, too. Also.. Max broke a pink bracelet. He wishes, hmm? Along with every other guy who has been caught looking at my second 'pair of eyes'. Pretty sad.

HALLOWEEN IS COMING, MY BITCHES. I will be so sexy, you'll be blinded. And. I talked to Betsy today. So I'm like, 'Yay!'. That's all for now. Let's hope Andy gets better, poor baby. Haha. And I think I'm going to buy that ringtone. I want it really bad. GO AKON/YOUNG JEEZY!

PEACE OUT.

HAPPY 14th BIRTHDAY AUSTIN! Yes, it is my birthday. I had a grr-eat day at school today. Like frosted flakes. I got a candy bar. YES. A LIMITED EDITION candy bar from Andy. And a birthday card from Kenzie-poo, and I got sang to in Social Studies. And somewhat in Math. And then Andy wrote, "Happy Birthday Austin!" On the math board. Yay. OH YEAH. And I freaking remembered for once, and I brought a camera. I got some great pictures. John, Bethanyy, Andy, Kenzie, the whole crew. I can't wait for them to be devoloped. No word on what I got OFFICALLY for my birthday yet (parents, family, blah blah) But I'll find out when my dad gets home. I am going out to eat at Bubba Gump's Shrimp tonight, I'll edit and say what I got. I can't wait for Friday. SAW 2, bitches! With Andy & John. It'll be kick-butt. Hmm.. also. I got my school pictures back. Not. Pretty. I swear, they are the worst pictures I have ever seen in my life. You have to see them to believe me. My eyes are too squinted, my bangs royally suck, and I look like I'm biting my lip. My mom will be pissed off. She hates my hair when I wear it like that. Pfft. Well, will edit l8er. EDITED: I am so damn tired. And my stomach hurts like hell. I ate too much. And all that shrimp, bread, and Dr. Pepper float is going to turn into flab. Since I didn't eat anything else all day. I got a few more 'happy birthdays', played with my NEW CELL PHONE. That's right, new cell. It's a flip-phone, super sexy. Like me. HAHA. But um, my parents fought the whole time and my mom was depressed she didn't get me anything good for my birthday. She got me Degrassi. Like, she extended the cable so I could watch Degrassi everyday and she's getting me a hotel this weekend. And uhh. My sister got me a Saw shirt and the DVD, but yeah. She didn't give it to me yet since I was being a brat. Yay. Brat. Shakemaker2435: happy b day 2 u happy b day 2 u happy b day to austin happy b day 2 u Aww. I feel so special. Kenize, Bethany, Micah, Cassidy, and Brianna also instant messaged me with that. Thanks guys! I love you. But my stomach hurts like hell, and I left my camera at my dad's. My cake is a giant 14, FUNFETTI. Annnd.. that's about it. Good Birthday I guess. Now I'm waiting for FRIDAY. SAW II, BITCHES! Oww. My stomach. ):

October 26th is tomorrow.

That means my birthday! Haha. Happy 14th, AUUUUUUUSTIN. To myself. Yeah, let's see. Explore testing today. Like I need a fucking test to tell me what I should do when I'm older. I have taken it TWICE before, and you know what? They both said I'd do peachy as a police officer or some type of law enforcement. Get that low wage job out of my face. Jesus. BUT IF I WERE A COP, I'd have a doggy with me. Yes I would. And I'd carry a gun and be like.. "Hey bitch. I have a gun." Oh yeah. But I want to be a forensic scientist. Nobody understands. I bet I will be a cop too, hmm?

Anything else? Hmm. Jeramias is back at school I guess. So the lunch table is complete again, haha. Annnd. John had his period at lunch. HAHA. In his face. And that's about it. I have to run to the store and get a camera, so I can take hot photos and like. Show them to peeps in Wisconsin. Peace out, bitches.

Forgot the rest of the song.

Anyway, yeah. This kid in the beginning of the day told me I was pretty. Yeah. He's in all my classes, too. So akward. 

"Hey Austin."
"Yeah?"
"I think you're pretty."
"Really?"
"Yeah."
"Thank you."

It was something like that, then I left. Ehhhhh. Notice I wasn't I was shuffling thru my papers, and he was playing on his calculator the whole time. Noooo eye contact. Yeah, really. Akward.

ANYWAY. I wore this pink shirt today and obviously people forgot where my eyes were today. So that is nice. On another note, my birthday is in TWO days and Saw 2 comes out in FOUR days. GIVE ME A HOO-HAH. (Hoo-hah) AHAAHA. Did I ever tell you guys about this dude who said, "Want to see something silly?" And he was serious, talking to his friends. I burst out laughing, now I say it all the time. The hilarity level.

Oh yeah. New seats in English. MY SPOT WAS SUPPOSE to be with John, Andy, and Alex. BUT NO. I have to sit next to Garrett, Trevor, and Max. Max isn't bad, but Garrett reeks. Reeks. Annoying. And reeks. So I am ticked about that. I really am. See, we chose popsicle sticks and the seat you want to sit at. BY nobody would pick the spot next to John, so when it came to my turn I got picked to sit next to fatty. MY SPOT IS WHERE BECCA IS SITTING. Rawr. That ruined my day right there. BUT HEY. John got my Math done. YAY. <33 I'm kind of hyper. Wee.

Domino = AWESOME. omgz, it was a REALLY good movie. Yeah, it was. I'll add that to my favorites list of movies. I didn't think it would be that good, Keira Knightly did awesome. I'd reccomend. Oh my. My birthday is creeping up pretty soon. I don't care, acutally. Nothing is going to go on in the first place. I just want my cellphone. Yeah. It goes b-day, Saw 2, Halloween. I don't even have a costume for Halloween to top it off. I think I'm going to hand out candy, I'm becoming an older brat. Too old for parties, and too old for trick or treating. And on Halloween, it's Micah's birthday. Yaaaaaay. I love Micah. xoxoxoxo OH YEAH. And I got new shoes. They are sexy. Yay, shoes. Don't worry Betsy & Emily, I love you guys too. I might do something this coming Saturday though. Who knows, I just hope John got my homework done. If he didn't, I'll rip his English up. GURANTEED. Other than that, I really have nothing to say. I've been on the computer for my four-day weekend, and I really don't want to go back to school. I have no energyyyyy. It is drained out of me. Maybe I can sit on it all week with my Webcam so Micah can beg. HAHA. Shh, I never said that. Well I'm going to go. Tori is pissing me off, as usual. Little bitch. omgz, Austin P.S. I'm thirsty. ): And I want Pizza Hut. P.S.S. Your password is too easy to guess. It's recommended that you change it, otherwise you risk having your journal hijacked. Visit http://www.livejournal.com/changepassword.bml to change your password. Oh, damn.

Pretty good day I guess. I switched homework with John, but shh. That's a secret. Hmm, let's see. I didn't do much else, really. But I got a new pickup line. Alright,

<u>Nice legs. When are they open?</u>

Ahh, yes. Shame I haven't heard that one until today. What a compliment! I acutally hate my legs. Mmm, celulite. I have a C+ in English? Got to boost that up to the A+ I deserve, bitch. Um. Math I gotz my work in. Hopefully I will get it in on Monday too. Johnny-cakes. 

..Let's see. I was going to go up to Wisconsin for my special 'four day' weekend. But I decided not to, just chill at home. But I always wanted to like have a party. It just seems so fun in the movies, until you get busted by the po-po or someone starts raping someone else. Pot, someone pukes, parents come home. Yadda, yadda. Wow. I'm such a dork. Plus my mom would kill me, I am serious. I'd never see the light of day again. I'm all pale and shit, skin & bones, and my mom is whipping me. I can see it all now. Living in the closet. Dreamy!

I heard something else today like my boobs were bigger than _____. I can't remember though. THE JOYS OF HANGING OUT WITH GUYS. Oh yes. John, Andy, Max, Evan, all that. That reminds me, I'm partners with Evan in Science. I see an F in the future. Ahaha, just kidding. ..I'm cold. Brr. I also threw a pen in Andy's eye today. Pretty damn funny if you ask me.

Anything else? Nope, there is not. Seeya later bitches. I have to go open my legs. Wish me luck on my four-day weekend. WITH THE HOUSE TO MYSELF. OH YEAH. Mall of America tomorrow too, with my daddy-o; I'm getting a flapper outfit. I have no clue what the fuck I am doing for Halloween though. Free candy? Party? Nothing?
